hopobject.body: this post is fantastic allmax vitastack vs orange triad Gunplay doesn't tend to happen that way, whether it's the shooting being done by Bad Guy or the shooting done by Good Guys (generally law enforcement). Cops get shot, sometimes killed. Bad Guy, it turns out, is more than just Bad – he has a life story that does not in any way justify the terror he has wreaked, but which could give us insight into how to keep tragedies from happening again, if we bothered to pay attention.
